text: OSU, Osu, or osu can stand for: ==Universities== * Ohio State University, Columbus, Ohio * Oklahoma State University–Stillwater * Oregon State University in Corvallis, Oregon ==Places== * Osu, Accra, a district in Ghana ** Osu Castle * Ōsu, a district of Nagoya, Japan *Ohio State University Airport, IATA airport code: OSU ==Other uses== * osu!, a freeware game developed by Dean Herbert, inspired by Osu!
